<p>Hello <%= @family_invitation.name.capitalize %>,

<p>
You are receiving this email because <%= @family_invitation.sender.full_name %>
  wants you to join their family on White Board!
</p>

<p>
  In order to become a member of the <%= @family_invitation.family.name %> family,
  please first create an account on WhiteBoard by <%= link_to "going here.", new_session_url %>
