  and paste in this token in the 'Join Family' form.<br />

  <strong>Token:</strong><pre> <%= @family_invitation.invite_token %> </pre>
</p>

<p>
  Have fun with using White Board!  We hope it makes your life easier
  and creates a better experience for you and the whole family.
</p>

